flowchart TB
  client[Web client] --> gw{{API gateway}}
  gw --> auth & catalog & cart

  subgraph services [Core services]
    direction TB
    auth[Auth service]
    catalog[Catalog service]
    cart[Cart service]
  end

  auth --> authdb[(Auth DB)]
  catalog --> catdb[(Catalog DB)]
  cart -.-> cache[(Redis cache)]
  cart ==> orders[Order service]
  orders --> queue[[Event queue]]

  classDef db fill:#fff3d6,stroke:#caa54a,color:#111
  class authdb,catdb,cache db
